#: ../../source/info/searchEngine.rst:2
msgid "搜索引擎利用"
msgstr "Search Engine Usage"

#: ../../source/info/searchEngine.rst:3
msgid "恰当地使用搜索引擎（Google/Bing/Yahoo/Baidu等）可以获取目标站点的较多信息。"
msgstr ""
"Using search engines properly, such as Google, Bing, Yahoo, and Baidu, can "
"reveal substantial information about a target site."

#: ../../source/info/searchEngine.rst:6
msgid "搜索引擎处理流程"
msgstr "Search Engine Processing Flow"

#: ../../source/info/searchEngine.rst:7
msgid "数据预处理"
msgstr "Data preprocessing"

#: ../../source/info/searchEngine.rst:8
msgid "长度截断"
msgstr "Length truncation"

#: ../../source/info/searchEngine.rst:9
msgid "大小写转化"
msgstr "Case conversion"

#: ../../source/info/searchEngine.rst:10
msgid "去标点符号"
msgstr "Punctuation removal"

#: ../../source/info/searchEngine.rst:11
msgid "简繁转换"
msgstr "Simplified/traditional Chinese conversion"

#: ../../source/info/searchEngine.rst:12
msgid "数字归一化，中文数字、阿拉伯数字、罗马字"
msgstr "Number normalization, including Chinese numerals, Arabic numerals, and Roman numerals"

#: ../../source/info/searchEngine.rst:13
msgid "同义词改写"
msgstr "Synonym rewriting"

#: ../../source/info/searchEngine.rst:14
msgid "拼音改写"
msgstr "Pinyin rewriting"

#: ../../source/info/searchEngine.rst:15
msgid "处理"
msgstr "Processing"

#: ../../source/info/searchEngine.rst:16
msgid "分词"
msgstr "Tokenization"

#: ../../source/info/searchEngine.rst:17
msgid "关键词抽取"
msgstr "Keyword extraction"

#: ../../source/info/searchEngine.rst:18
msgid "非法信息过滤"
msgstr "Illegal content filtering"

#: ../../source/info/searchEngine.rst:21
msgid "搜索技巧"
msgstr "Search Techniques"

#: ../../source/info/searchEngine.rst:22
msgid "site:www.hao123.com"
msgstr "site:www.hao123.com"

#: ../../source/info/searchEngine.rst:23
msgid "返回此目标站点被搜索引擎抓取收录的所有内容"
msgstr "Return all content from the target site that has been crawled and indexed by the search engine"

#: ../../source/info/searchEngine.rst:24
msgid "site:www.hao123.com keyword"
msgstr "site:www.hao123.com keyword"

#: ../../source/info/searchEngine.rst:25
msgid "返回此目标站点被搜索引擎抓取收录的包含此关键词的所有页面"
msgstr "Return all indexed pages on the target site that contain the keyword"

#: ../../source/info/searchEngine.rst:26
msgid "此处可以将关键词设定为网站后台，管理后台，密码修改，密码找回等"
msgstr "The keyword can be set to terms such as website backend, admin panel, password change, or password recovery"

#: ../../source/info/searchEngine.rst:27
msgid "site:www.hao123.com inurl:admin.php"
msgstr "site:www.hao123.com inurl:admin.php"

#: ../../source/info/searchEngine.rst:28
msgid "返回目标站点的地址中包含admin.php的所有页面，可以使用admin.php/manage.php或者其他关键词来寻找关键功能页面"
msgstr ""
"Return all pages on the target site whose URLs contain admin.php. Keywords "
"such as admin.php, manage.php, or other terms can be used to find important "
"function pages."

#: ../../source/info/searchEngine.rst:29
msgid "link:www.hao123.com"
msgstr "link:www.hao123.com"

#: ../../source/info/searchEngine.rst:30
msgid "返回所有包含目标站点链接的页面，其中包括其开发人员的个人博客，开发日志，或者开放这个站点的第三方公司，合作伙伴等"
msgstr ""
"Return pages that contain links to the target site, including developers' "
"personal blogs, development logs, third-party companies involved in the site,"
" partners, and similar sources."

#: ../../source/info/searchEngine.rst:31
msgid "related:www.hao123.com"
msgstr "related:www.hao123.com"

#: ../../source/info/searchEngine.rst:32
msgid "返回所有与目标站点”相似”的页面，可能会包含一些通用程序的信息等"
msgstr "Return pages that are \"similar\" to the target site, which may include information about common applications or frameworks"

#: ../../source/info/searchEngine.rst:33
msgid "intitle:\"500 Internal Server Error\" \"server at\""
msgstr "intitle:\"500 Internal Server Error\" \"server at\""

#: ../../source/info/searchEngine.rst:34
msgid "搜索出错的页面"
msgstr "Search for error pages"

#: ../../source/info/searchEngine.rst:35
msgid "inurl:\"nph-proxy.cgi\" \"Start browsing\""
msgstr "inurl:\"nph-proxy.cgi\" \"Start browsing\""

#: ../../source/info/searchEngine.rst:36
msgid "查找代理服务器"
msgstr "Find proxy servers"

#: ../../source/info/searchEngine.rst:38
msgid ""
"除了以上的关键字，还有allintile / allinurl / allintext / inanchor / intext  / "
"filetype / info / numberange / cache等。"
msgstr ""
"In addition to the keywords above, there are also allintile / allinurl / "
"allintext / inanchor / intext / filetype / info / numberange / cache, and "
"others."

#: ../../source/info/searchEngine.rst:41
msgid "通配符"
msgstr "Wildcards"

#: ../../source/info/searchEngine.rst:42
msgid "``*`` 代表某一个单词"
msgstr "``*`` represents a single word"

#: ../../source/info/searchEngine.rst:43
msgid "OR 或者 | 代表逻辑或"
msgstr "OR or | represents logical OR"

#: ../../source/info/searchEngine.rst:44
msgid "单词前跟 ``+`` 表强制查询"
msgstr "A ``+`` before a word forces that term to be included in the query"

#: ../../source/info/searchEngine.rst:45
msgid "单词前跟 ``-`` 表排除对应关键字"
msgstr "A ``-`` before a word excludes the corresponding keyword"

#: ../../source/info/searchEngine.rst:46
msgid "``\"`` 强调关键字"
msgstr "``\"`` emphasizes a keyword"

#: ../../source/info/searchEngine.rst:49
msgid "tips"
msgstr "Tips"

#: ../../source/info/searchEngine.rst:50
msgid "查询不区分大小写"
msgstr "Queries are case-insensitive"

#: ../../source/info/searchEngine.rst:51
msgid "括号会被忽略"
msgstr "Parentheses are ignored"

#: ../../source/info/searchEngine.rst:52
msgid "默认用 and 逻辑进行搜索"
msgstr "Searches use AND logic by default"

#: ../../source/info/searchEngine.rst:55
msgid "快照"
msgstr "Snapshots"

#: ../../source/info/searchEngine.rst:56
msgid "搜索引擎的快照中也常包含一些关键信息，如程序报错信息可以会泄漏网站具体路径，或者一些快照中会保存一些测试用的测试信息，比如说某个网站在开发了后台功能模块的时候，还没给所有页面增加权限鉴别，此时被搜索引擎抓取了快照，即使后来网站增加了权限鉴别，但搜索引擎的快照中仍会保留这些信息。"
msgstr ""
"Search engine snapshots often contain key information. For example, program "
"error messages may leak specific website paths, and some snapshots may "
"preserve test data. If a website was crawled while backend modules were still"
" being developed and not all pages had authorization checks, the search "
"engine snapshot may retain that information even after authorization checks "
"are added later."

#: ../../source/info/searchEngine.rst:58
msgid ""
"另外也有专门的站点快照提供快照功能，如 Wayback Machine 和 `Archive.org "
"<https://archive.org/>`_ 等。"
msgstr ""
"There are also dedicated site snapshot services, such as Wayback Machine and "
"`Archive.org <https://archive.org/>`_."

#: ../../source/info/searchEngine.rst:61
msgid "Github"
msgstr "GitHub"

#: ../../source/info/searchEngine.rst:62
msgid "在Github中，可能会存在源码泄露、AccessKey泄露、密码、服务器配置泄露等情况，常见的搜索技巧有："
msgstr ""
"GitHub may contain leaked source code, AccessKeys, passwords, server "
"configuration, and similar information. Common search techniques include:"

#: ../../source/info/searchEngine.rst:64
msgid "``@example.com password/pass/pwd/secret/credentials/token``"
msgstr "``@example.com password/pass/pwd/secret/credentials/token``"

#: ../../source/info/searchEngine.rst:65
msgid "``@example.com username/user/key/login/ftp/``"
msgstr "``@example.com username/user/key/login/ftp/``"

#: ../../source/info/searchEngine.rst:66
msgid "``@example.com config/ftp/smtp/pop``"
msgstr "``@example.com config/ftp/smtp/pop``"

#: ../../source/info/searchEngine.rst:67
msgid "``@example.com security_credentials/connetionstring``"
msgstr "``@example.com security_credentials/connetionstring``"

#: ../../source/info/searchEngine.rst:68
msgid "``@example.com JDBC/ssh2_auth_password/send_keys``"
msgstr "``@example.com JDBC/ssh2_auth_password/send_keys``"
